export const docsSections = [{"id":"ddisa-sso-login","title":"DDISA SSO login","html":"<p>Troop is a DDISA <strong>Service Provider</strong>. A user opens Troop, which discovers the\nuser&#39;s IdP from a DNS <code>_ddisa</code> TXT record and redirects them to authorize — no\npassword, no per-SP account.</p>\n<p>Troop&#39;s start page (the login email is right there):</p>\n<p><figure class=\"shot\"><figcaption class=\"shot-bar\"><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-label\">Troop landing</span></figcaption><img src=\"/docs/screenshots/05-troop-landing.png\" alt=\"Troop landing\" loading=\"lazy\"></figure></p>\n<p>The DDISA consent screen at the IdP — Troop is asking to use the user&#39;s\nidentity (shown once, then remembered):</p>\n<p><figure class=\"shot\"><figcaption class=\"shot-bar\"><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-label\">DDISA consent</span></figcaption><img src=\"/docs/screenshots/06-idp-authorize-troop.png\" alt=\"DDISA consent\" loading=\"lazy\"></figure></p>\n<p>Back on Troop, authenticated — the agents dashboard:</p>\n<p><figure class=\"shot\"><figcaption class=\"shot-bar\"><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-label\">Troop dashboard</span></figcaption><img src=\"/docs/screenshots/07-troop-dashboard.png\" alt=\"Troop dashboard\" loading=\"lazy\"></figure></p>\n"},{"id":"agent-lifecycle-spawn-run-destroy","title":"Agent lifecycle — spawn → run → destroy","html":"<p>The full control-plane round-trip: a <strong>nest</strong> daemon binds to Troop, then an\nagent is spawned, run (it answers a chat message through its LLM), and\ndestroyed — all driven through Troop.</p>\n<p>Spawned — the agent appears in the dashboard:</p>\n<p><figure class=\"shot\"><figcaption class=\"shot-bar\"><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-label\">Agent spawned</span></figcaption><img src=\"/docs/screenshots/agent-01-spawned.png\" alt=\"Agent spawned\" loading=\"lazy\"></figure></p>\n<p>Run — the owner sends a message and the agent replies through Troop; the\nreply proves the spawn → bridge → LLM → reply path end-to-end:</p>\n<p><figure class=\"shot\"><figcaption class=\"shot-bar\"><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-label\">Agent ran</span></figcaption><img src=\"/docs/screenshots/agent-02-ran.png\" alt=\"Agent ran\" loading=\"lazy\"></figure></p>\n<p>Destroyed — the agent is torn down and the dashboard is empty again:</p>\n<p><figure class=\"shot\"><figcaption class=\"shot-bar\"><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-dot\"></span><span class=\"shot-label\">Agent destroyed</span></figcaption><img src=\"/docs/screenshots/agent-03-destroyed.png\" alt=\"Agent destroyed\" loading=\"lazy\"></figure></p>\n"}]
